## Proposed Changes

### 1. Authentication Infrastructure

New dependencies: `google-auth-library` (Google token exchange), `jose` (JWT signing/verification for cookies).

#### [NEW] [auth.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/lib/auth.ts)
- `createSession(user)` → Signs a JWT with user ID, sets it as an HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite cookie
- `getSession(request)` → Reads cookie, verifies JWT, returns user info
- `clearSession()` → Clears the auth cookie
- JWT payload: `{ userId, email, name, picture }`
- Cookie name: `session` with 7-day expiry, auto-refreshed on each request

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/auth/google/route.ts)
- [GET](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#7-25) → Redirects browser to Google OAuth consent URL
- Generates state parameter for CSRF protection, stores in cookie

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/auth/google/callback/route.ts)
- [GET](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#7-25) → Handles Google OAuth callback
- Exchanges authorization code for tokens using `google-auth-library`
- Extracts user profile from ID token (email, name, picture)
- Creates/updates `User` document in MongoDB
- Calls `createSession(user)` → sets cookie
- Redirects to `/`

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/auth/me/route.ts)
- [GET](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#7-25) → Returns current user info from session cookie (or 401)

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/auth/logout/route.ts)
- [POST](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#26-78) → Clears session cookie, returns 200

#### [NEW] [middleware.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/middleware.ts)
- Next.js middleware that protects all routes except `/login`, `/api/auth/*`, and static assets
- Reads session cookie → if invalid/missing, redirects to `/login`
- This avoids having to add auth checks to every individual API route

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/login/page.tsx)
