### 2. Database Schema Changes

#### [MODIFY] [models.ts](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/lib/models.ts)

**New models:**

**User**
- `email`: String (required, unique) — Google email
- [name](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/lib/hooks/use-shopping-list.tsx#108-116): String — display name from Google
- `picture`: String — avatar URL from Google
- `defaultListId`: ObjectId (ref: ShoppingList) — user's default list
- `createdAt`: Number (timestamp)

**ShoppingList**
- [name](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/lib/hooks/use-shopping-list.tsx#108-116): String (required) — list name (e.g., "Weekly Groceries")
- `ownerId`: ObjectId (ref: User, required) — creator/owner
- `createdAt`: Number (timestamp)

**ListMembership**
- `listId`: ObjectId (ref: ShoppingList, required)
- `userId`: ObjectId (ref: User, required)
- `role`: String (enum: `owner`, `member`) — owner has full control, member can add/complete items
- `joinedAt`: Number (timestamp)
- Compound unique index on [(listId, userId)](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#79-110)

**Invitation**
- `listId`: ObjectId (ref: ShoppingList, required)
- `inviterUserId`: ObjectId (ref: User, required)
- `inviteeEmail`: String (required) — email of the person being invited
- `status`: String (enum: `pending`, `accepted`, `rejected`)
- `createdAt`: Number (timestamp)
- Compound unique index on [(listId, inviteeEmail, status: 'pending')](file:///d:/code/weekly-shopping-list/src/app/api/items/route.ts#79-110)

**Modified models:**

**Item** — add `listId: ObjectId (ref: ShoppingList, required)`

**History** — add `userId: ObjectId (ref: User, required)` (item history is personal)

**PushSubscription** — add `userId: ObjectId (ref: User, required)` (notifications are per-user)

